<div class="page">
  <div class="page-header">
    <div>
      <h2 class="page-title">📞 Admin kontakt ma'lumotlari</h2>
      <p class="page-sub">Sovg'a tasdiqlanganda xaridor shu raqam/nik orqali siz bilan bog'lanadi</p>
    </div>
    <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/gifts">← Sovg'alar</a>
  </div>

  {{#if saved}}<div class="alert alert-success">✅ Saqlandi</div>{{/if}}

  <div class="card" style="max-width:480px">
    <form method="POST" action="/gifts/settings/contact">
      <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom:20px">
        <label class="field">
          <span class="field-label">📱 Admin telefon raqami</span>
          <input class="input" type="tel" name="phone" value="{{phone}}"
                 placeholder="+998901234567" style="max-width:300px" />
          <span class="field-hint">Xaridor tasdiqlangach shu raqamni ko'radi</span>
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom:24px">
        <label class="field">
          <span class="field-label">✈️ Telegram nik (username)</span>
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;max-width:300px">
            <span style="color:var(--text-secondary);font-size:1.1rem">@</span>
            <input class="input" type="text" name="telegram" value="{{telegram}}"
                   placeholder="username" style="flex:1" />
          </div>
          <span class="field-hint">@ belgisisiz kiriting, masalan: myshop_admin</span>
        </label>
      </div>

      <div style="display:flex;gap:10px">
        <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">💾 Saqlash</button>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/gifts">Bekor qilish</a>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="max-width:480px;margin-top:16px;background:var(--bg-secondary,#f8f9fa)">
    <p style="margin:0;font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--text-secondary)">
      <b>Namuna xabar (tasdiqlangach user ga yuboriladi):</b><br><br>
      ✅ Tabriklaymiz! "Sovg'a nomi" sovg'angiz tasdiqlandi.<br><br>
      {{#if phone}}📱 Tel: {{phone}}<br>{{/if}}
      {{#if telegram}}✈️ Telegram: @{{telegram}}{{/if}}
      {{#unless phone}}{{#unless telegram}}<i style="color:#aaa">Kontakt kiritilmagan</i>{{/unless}}{{/unless}}
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
